Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們向第七界層前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把前六個界層\N恢復了和平的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然通過彩虹\N升上了第七界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因為多惡達的佈置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們迷失了在\N一個叫魔幻境的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入了第三道門魔天門\N我和火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即掉進了魔天門的底層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要離開這裏就要登上\N在高高的天空上的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.63,0:02:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在爬山、上樓梯的時候\N雖想放棄過幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.27,0:02:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但和火美子一起努力\N終於上到天上的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把魔天門的守護魔神艾利根\N打倒後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只剩下最後的第四道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十六話\N好孩子?壞孩子?魔界門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是魔幻地獄門\N最後的門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.71,0:02:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這是最後的門了\N不要因為能來到這裏就得意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.82,0:03:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能通過這道門的人\N自創界山有史以來從未出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我就來改良歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是自動門啊\N去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.75,0:03:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多門呢,我要數數看\N一、二、三…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡惡開心,登登登…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.88,0:04:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有誰在呢\N奇怪了,心理作用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你很慢啊\N現在來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡惡開心,登登登…\N做壞事是很快樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.77,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我數到多少呢?忘記了!\N渡,我要再去數一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒有這種空閒呢\N你再這樣數我就留下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,緊追之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壞孩子是有活力的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有做壞事才會快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你走慢點啊\N我數不到門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡惡開心,登登登…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好煩啊!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好、很好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.78,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是四萬…有很多呢,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,你竟打我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,普通的反擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍者受過訓練\N被打時會立即還擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還未打中你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡的表情好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今為止,我都搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.04,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是屬於多惡達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成了壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是忍法分身術嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?原來是兩個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是魔界門的守門人\N明王哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是同樣的明王弟弟\N我們是同一日出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說是孿生兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可愛呢,畫上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已幫你畫了\N就要聽我們說明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在通過門的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就會在他耳邊\N不斷叫他做壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.99,0:06:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通過全部門的時候你們已經\N變成多惡達大人的部下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼事也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中也會有些特別體質的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N你已忠誠於多惡達大人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全心全意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會為了\N支配創界山而戰吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外還有別的事幹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.18,0:06:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那你跟我們來吧\N我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.23,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,做壞事很快樂吧?\N非常愉快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這魔力去到哪裏也不會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!婆婆\N渡,你完全變成壞人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是稱讚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.92,0:07:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,為了紀念你變成壞人\N特別給你看些好東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是魔時計嗎?明王兄弟\N我們來看死亡表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見同伴內心也不會轉變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,到底怎麼了?\N沒什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.68,0:08:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!\N不要隨便叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.78,0:08:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通過了魔界門\N就連內心也變成魔界的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.82,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?渡\N我們在等你救我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真囉嗦,不要說過不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,快些清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已非常清醒了,你這猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你是創界山的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義的朋友\N這個世界的勇者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣?想被救世主的劍\N把頭斬下來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你不斬\N我們很快也會被時針斬掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然丸子還是一邊\N看死刑一邊吃才好味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N不要跳這麼無聊的舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有更有趣的東西了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,把時針的針調快\N你說怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很好呢,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那就讓我們兄弟來報時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,拜託你說得有型點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是5時59分35秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.50,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是5時59分30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,令渡清醒啊\N渡,現在是清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對\N令他從壞人中清醒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡是壞孩子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,現在的渡是壞孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡是壞孩子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離死亡時間還有20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.09,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有10秒\N8秒,7秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…\N囉嗦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是為了什麼來到這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有5秒\N渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想想創界山的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了壞事的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有四秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這時候在下怎樣也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.41,0:10:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但求你現在記起\N正義的心一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3、2…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!\N喂,火美子,壞孩子快飛走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎?\N壞念頭很快就會進入人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候就想起老婆婆的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一定會變回好孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.78,0:10:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,那個方法啊\N好,渡,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.22,0:10:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壞孩子快飛走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,世伯!\N渡,你醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡。你終於清醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是在下的徒弟\N我的方法有效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟被這幼稚的方法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時計雖然可以推進\N但卻不可以停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非你通過了魔幻地獄門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.38,0:11:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你的關係\N令時間減少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻婆婆婆,出口在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會讓你通過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.53,0:12:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是明王哥哥\N我是明王弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集齊二人就無敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看哪處?\N這邊啊,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們力量不及它,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成龍王丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你看看我們的厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金波士,金波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸,快跳起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會讓你成功嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炎龍拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見了,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!鳳凰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊!這邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳雷炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,好,再來一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續機關炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,擊倒他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.13,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題,龍王丸\N就這樣子裝成掉下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N要令他們大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,雖然危險,試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續下去太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.64,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不夠,要再接近地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去,掉下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,是時候了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.82,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第四條鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N那是魔幻地獄門出口的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,快點啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是這些鑰匙內\N其中一條…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來有這小手腳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡很聰明呢\N是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小渡…\N我現在立即開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.78,0:17:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有些形狀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,這個要對得準確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…北是上面\N東是哪一邊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.58,0:18:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到你弄完後我已死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,東是右邊啊\N好,是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.91,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!通過魔幻地獄門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓你們有命離開嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還連著呢\N好重,快走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親…\N渡,火美子,做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不算得上什麼?\N我只是出了點力就是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是紫龍啊\N紫龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個麻婆婆婆嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕是多惡達的魔力\N令她變成那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你去救出聖龍妃和翔龍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖龍妃和翔龍子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是創界山的女王和她的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.87,0:20:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個創界山是由女王聖龍妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.34,0:20:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從第七界層開始\N帶給這裏和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七色的彩虹就是證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.78,0:20:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是保護著女王的七色龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻化成的神部七龍神的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.72,0:20:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他們二人現在\N被多惡達的魔神幽禁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一日不救出他們\N就不能令創界山恢復和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了\N我一定會打倒多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他們二人救出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你去找龍王之劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王之劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.51,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是唯一能打倒多惡達的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那把劍在什麼地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該就在第七界層\N的某個地方纔對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某個地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.22,0:20:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定能找出來的\N沒有那把劍就打不倒多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了\N總之我們上第七界層吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N通往第七界層的彩虹在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個呢…\N從剛才起我就開始找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四處也沒有呢\N喂!彩虹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有彩虹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…\N請看那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.01,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第七界層的底部\N只能從那裏上地面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七界層有一條白龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.99,0:21:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白龍手上的龍神之盾\N能壓制多惡達的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當龍神之盾和龍王之劍\N也得到手的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.07,0:21:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說的救世主就會成為真實\N也可令我們神部七龍神甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.81,0:21:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七界層現在是個\N很可怕的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.01,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預防萬一,你拿這個去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:22:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,紫龍

